<h1 class='h1 h1--alt m2'>
War
</h1>

</div>

<div class='row'>
<div class='col col-lg-sidebarred'>
<!-- PB:B: copy --><div class='p2'>
<p>A collection of TED Talks (and more) on the topic of war.</p>

</div>



<!-- PB:B: dynamic -->
<div class='section section--minor'>
