<div class='media__message'>
<div class='copy text-left'>
<h4 class="h7 m5">Minescape</h4>

<p><strong>by Brett Van Ort</strong><br>
Photojournalist Brett Van Ort blends images of deceptively innocent landscapes, land mines, and prosthetic limbs to illustrate the remnant threats of war that linger in times of peace.<br>
<strong><a href="http://geni.us/41h?track=topics">Buy now</a></strong></p>

